1987年，Takai 将反应拓展至无卤烯烃的合成。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=(''E'')-Selective olefination of aldehydes by means of ''gem''-dichromium reagents derived by reduction of ''gem''-diiodoalkanes with chromium(II) chloride|author=T. Okazoe, Kazuhiko Takai, K. Utimoto|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1987|volume=109|issue=3|pages=951–953|doi=10.1021/ja00237a081}}</ref>

